{"tid":1483772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"潑婦KOL食女義士人血饅頭","createTime":"2019-08-18T13:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T13:43:22.000Z","uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0bd03f3fa0f61e21c0bc9d81fe9ea89851d47a3","tid":1483772,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSfRbpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSfRbpv.jpg&h=5d9f184e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02JjkdW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02JjkdW.jpg&h=8609ecd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你話連衛兵我都由你，乜撚野汝等蟻民呀，自己乜野咁撚巴閉呀，你老味21世紀人人平等你仲學人講蟻民 覺得自己高人一等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/juxgnzp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjuxgnzp.png&h=8c48be4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係個得果2萬人嘅群組，每隔幾個鐘就post女義士單野刷存在感，人地唔認同你就叫人含撚，人地比晒証據你你就話人改圖講大話。而家連陳沛然醫生都比你追擊埋，人地一個人抗衝成個醫管局，你做過啲乜呀，用陳醫生刷存在感，少少野咬撚住人地唔放</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嘩！等女義士好返之後同女義士袁子威想屌佢隻眼？知唔知咩叫二次傷害呀！做人咪撚咁刻薄啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不如你直接女義士講：而家有人想屌你隻眼呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KU7L0gf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKU7L0gf.png&h=c8916772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持呂麗瑤？你炒撚晒車呀！你有冇可憐下個教練比人屈？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbhPHuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbhPHuS.png&h=75c11537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘩！原來北京先係你屋企喎！咁撚愛國返去住啦，咪黎香港！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇你個樣都似果啲細細個比人恰 而家要恰返人黎滿足自己，個人咪撚咁小學雞啦。"},{"pid":"d133141a7454b07119850a42d146f573ddfbf492","tid":1483772,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyt0ecz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgyt0ecz.jpg&h=e159e9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌 隔夜飯都嘔撚晒出黎"},{"pid":"8a723cf27c0a8626b62835431d491f6d2cdc88f5","tid":1483772,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae08183c336d986e68beafce0d4bfc2c3307101","tid":1483772,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f8668e71c65eda60b57b33e28db533ad9820fc","tid":1483772,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"食緊野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff19816721d46aa01bb6db07d8ea840a121bf084","tid":1483772,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f8668e71c65eda60b57b33e28db533ad9820fc","tid":1483772,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"食緊野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"那麼醜的妞"},{"pid":"994d790a4eda9d102b1a23631faa405f40e13d3e","tid":1483772,"uid":141131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"都話唔使幫啲豬閪宣傳咯"},{"pid":"f27c5d333665fff10b54fbbb7e335429387fa8a6","tid":1483772,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994d790a4eda9d102b1a23631faa405f40e13d3e","tid